title: Sovereign Grace Discography 2000-2012 (11 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SOVEREIGN GRACE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 11 releases...

 * 2000 - King Of Grace
 * 2001 - No Greater Love
 * 2003 - Upward - The Bob Kauflin Hymns Project
 * 2008 - Come Weary Saints
 * 2008 - Psalms
 * 2009 - Sons And Daughters
 * 2011 - Risen
 * 2011 - The Gathering - Live From Worship God
 * 2012 - From Age To Age
 * 2012 - From Age To Age - Accompaniment Tracks
 * 2012 - Together For The Gospel Live II

Sovereign Grace (Sovereign Grace Music and Sovereign Grace Ministries) produces Christ-exalting music and training for local churches.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
